{"tid":684382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 日本巡邏機驚見 中國、北韓船隻疑海上走私","createTime":"2018-05-30T13:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T14:56:07.000Z","uid":31637,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"661684dcb3648d8a61106a260e0e030fd2483dac","tid":684382,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:13:41.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日本外務省及防衛省今（29）日向聯合國通報，有中國小型船隻於2018年5月19日，航出東海進入公海範圍，並靠近1艘北韓油輪，雙方恐係在從事非法走私，全程都被日本海上自衛隊的P-3C巡邏機拍攝下來。<br />\n<br />\n根據《共同社》報導，日本P-3C反潛巡邏機19日在距離中國上海市東南方350公里、超出東海範圍的公海上，發現1艘疑插有紅色中國5星旗的小型船隻，與1艘北韓籍油輪在海上橫靠，互相連上船舶固定軟管，可能是在進行物資走私，日方對此亦向中國政府通報。<br />\n<br />\n北韓目前仍受到聯合國安理會制裁，禁止成員國船隻進入北韓港口，或讓北韓船隻停泊港口，日本已在2018年目擊5起向北韓船隻走私物資的事件，日方無法證實中國船隻在19日有實際作出走私行為，但研判雙方從事走私的機率非常大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2441554\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2441554&d=C5tuzVbK%2Fw0HjkR772TvCk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=ade820b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2441554&h=e210efb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2441554</a>"},{"pid":"5fc33015d038a85198116f425cbc1a084090c013","tid":684382,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:14:31.000Z","msg":"搞屎棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb99127c5a0a3f4aafe1d768d6d4943ae0080a8","tid":684382,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:15:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3796a622db522ca92583fcfc04e0bd65aaed3e4b","tid":684382,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n制裁埋贏国呀笨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />